Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles (001 - 037 + Annual) (2011 - Ongoing) (digital) (Minutemen-Faessla+Empire) 


They're BACK! This summer, the original heroes in a half-shell make a triumphant return to comics! Leonardo, Donatello, Michaelangelo, and Raphael reunite to bring their ninja aptitude and teenage attitude to IDW Publishing in this all-new, action-packed series.
